得好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d37a6e4a8ea0957c48ad6cbeb70c8c8191aa5d3","tid":2020414,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T21:33:47.000Z","msg":"戒J Telegram群<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FEMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=9e06a548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/EMOE2Ulb4sxDctTi6g3A-A</a><br />\n<br />\n中醫：腎虛百病叢生<br />\n精由腎儲藏，而精既作用係用黎滋潤五臟六腑，所以丁得多會導致整個五臟六腑變差，就會出現好多症狀。<br />\n每射一次就傷身一次，包括做愛，夢遺（含精量唔多），而節制打Ｊ只不過係延遲你出症狀既時間／嚴重程度。<br />\n<br />\n每人體質唔同，症狀都唔同，以下為最常見：<br />\n早洩，變樣哀，猥瑣，臉色灰暗，自卑冇自信、腰痛<br />\n腦力下降，暗瘡，有口氣，脫髮、耳嗚、任何神經症<br />\n體臭，易怒，夜尿，表達能力差，社交恐懼症，雙眼無神，前列線炎<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n戒為良藥<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2F2&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=11e56612\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/2</a><br />\n戒J 前後對比圖<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.noj1314.258club.com%2Fforumdisplay.php%3Ffid%3D63&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=99246c63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.noj1314.258club.com/forumdisplay.php?fid=63</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ需知： <br />\n<br />\n戒Ｊ後３個月內症狀加重／加深屬正常，係戒斷反應<br />\n<br />\n身體恢復過程並唔係直線上升，而係好似過山車咁上下移動，會不斷由壞轉好，好轉壞<br />\n但隨著時間既增長，身體會慢慢恢復，症狀慢慢消失<br />\n<br />\n夢遺唔當破戒，意淫都傷身，睇ＡＶ唔Ｊ一樣咁傷身 ，中醫：心動則精自走<br />\n<br />\n做愛都傷身，所以我地戒Ｊ恢復身體，身體好虧既戒返２年，之後再節制性行為，咁就唔會出症狀，飛翔老師推薦一月2次，就是腎氣充足的情況下，這樣對身體傷害較小。<br />\n<br />\n戒色唔係做和尚，係先禁慾養返好個身體，再同老婆／女友節制性生活，咁就唔會出症狀<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁期間扑野唔算破戒，但你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒"},{"pid":"a433594b838853453536acd6b85e9fe53366ad22","tid":2020414,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5ec3565ec9371efda806bfa15906dfb3f8806fa","tid":2020414,"uid":169116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T04:58:35.000Z","msg":"無野最多甩頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T20:10:58.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"54b417939fd9a1471a0e9108def8748899c2834a","tid":2020414,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T20:22:31.000Z","msg":"三日打五十次先正常"},{"pid":"e3eec495d86f5b0d9d58bf6d4c653298674f2c55","tid":2020414,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b37646bd13466abb178b545bd822fb3ec422edb","tid":2020414,"uid":304179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"343ffef3db8e62a97cb279dd8f33a0caa8aa4b36","tid":2020414,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"琴晚都三次&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T20:26:04.000Z","msg":"覺得好攰即係個身體話你知頂唔順 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eedb8b391b48fb3ed453f3c3932d91ec9db6d52","tid":2020414,"uid":245484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T20:34:50.000Z","msg":"太少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n建議去驗下係咪腎虧"}]}